{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Create the ultimate beachfront destination! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/extras/clouds_aspectratio.gif?t=1739972401\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game all about building a beautiful boardwalk.\u00a0 Start with small stands and grow into a sprawling seaside paradise full of rides, high-end shops and fancy restaurants. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/extras/build_aspectratio.gif?t=1739972401\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build</strong> <strong>your boardwalk piece by piece</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dozens of shops to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build rides, restaurants, and stores, selling everything from sunglasses to vintage video games to sea glass art.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/extras/manage_aspectratio.gif?t=1739972401\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Manage</strong> <strong>your shops to optimize your boardwalk's income</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Influence the revenue and popularity of each shop by customizing it's product or service</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Promote shops to bring in more visitors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adjust the amount of staff each shop has</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/extras/combine_aspectratio.gif?t=1739972401\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Combine shops and rides to create new ones</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As your shops grow in level from customer visits, combine them to create bigger, better shops. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn fame points the more customers visit, and unlock new combinations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/extras/watch_aspectratio.gif?t=1739972401\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Other Features: </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Respond to demand-changing events such as bad weather or neighboring competition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Participate in festivals to boost income and draw in big crowds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do well enough and you might even attract VIPs to give your boardwalk a huge boost and unlock top-tier attractions</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2958890?t=1739972401","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739972401","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/32493a350caa2addb8f6565860fde6d4a0f5a2d3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739972401","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/32493a350caa2addb8f6565860fde6d4a0f5a2d3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739972401","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Create the ultimate beachfront destination! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958890/extras/clouds_aspectratio.gif?t=1739972401\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game all about buildin